public abstract void setInput(java.lang.Object input)
Sets the input to this editor. This method simply updates the internal member variables of the editor.

Parameters:

refresh

public abstract void refresh()
Refreshes this editor with information freshly obtained from the editor's model. This method is called by the main editor whenever a command on the command stack has been called. It is up to the subclasses to determine what needs to be refreshed.
